---
---
<section class="py-[100px] px-[5%] bg-bg" id="beneficios">
    <div class="text-center max-w-[700px] mx-auto mb-16 fade-up">
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-heading font-semibold leading-tight mb-6">Por qué elegir nuestros <br>gorros terapéuticos</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-text-light">Diseñados por expertos con empatía y tecnología textil para tu bienestar.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-[repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr))] gap-10 max-w-[1200px] mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_4px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(200,140,149,0.1)] hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 text-center fade-up delay-[100ms]">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                <i class="ph-light ph-hand-heart text-[2.5rem] text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-heading mb-3">Suavidad Extrema</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light">Costuras invisibles y tejidos diseñados específicamente para pieles sensibles post-tratamiento.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_4px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(200,140,149,0.1)] hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 text-center fade-up delay-[200ms]">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                <i class="ph-light ph-shield-star text-[2.5rem] text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-heading mb-3">Protección Total</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light">Cobertura perfecta que protege contra los rayos UV y el entorno, asegurando tranquilidad.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-10 rounded-3xl shadow-[0_4px_6px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] hover:shadow-[0_10px_30px_rgba(200,140,149,0.1)] hover:-translate-y-2 transition-all duration-300 text-center fade-up delay-[300ms]">
            <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
                <i class="ph-light ph-smiley text-[2.5rem] text-primary"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-heading mb-3">Cuidado del Autoestima</h3>
            <p class="text-text-light">Diseños modernos, elegantes y versátiles que te permiten expresar tu estilo personal.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
